## Project Structure

```
taskflow/
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ taskflow/
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ __init__.py    # Public exports
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ flow.py        # TaskFlow ‚Äì main interface
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ task.py        # Task model & TaskStatus enum
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ dag.py         # DAG builder, validator, cycle detection
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ scheduler.py   # Dependency-aware task scheduler
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ executor.py    # Thread / process worker pool
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ queue.py       # Thread-safe task queue
