## Architecture

```
TaskFlow.run()
    ‚îÇ
    ‚îú‚îÄ‚ñ∫ DAG.validate()          # cycle check, missing dep check
    ‚îÇ
    ‚îú‚îÄ‚ñ∫ Scheduler (thread)      # watches completed tasks, enqueues ready ones
    ‚îÇ       ‚îÇ
    ‚îÇ       ‚îî‚îÄ‚ñ∫ TaskQueue       # thread-safe FIFO
    ‚îÇ               ‚îÇ
    ‚îî‚îÄ‚ñ∫ Executor (thread)       # pulls from queue, submits to pool
            ‚îÇ
            ‚îú‚îÄ‚ñ∫ ThreadPoolExecutor  (mode="thread")
            ‚îî‚îÄ‚ñ∫ ProcessPoolExecutor (mode="process")
                    ‚îÇ
                    ‚îî‚îÄ‚ñ∫ RetryManager  # on failure: backoff + re-queue
```

